race.comment: BLOWIN' SMOKE (2) just missed two back at Mt Magnet before a 2.1L defeat at Geraldton most recently. He's probably outperformed his market expectation in both runs, and that sets him up nicely for this event. Ratings stack up and he can strike the knockout blow third-up. ZED HOT EXPRESS (3) will find this much easier than what she's been contesting lately at Kalgoorlie. The drop back to this level looks a smart move by connections and she gets in light after the claim of Webster. Can make her presence felt. SOLARIS GLOW (6) felt the pinch late first-up at Geraldton but she did jump a big price there. This is probably an easier race on paper and she maps well from an inside barrier. She won't be far away. REVOLVING (7) ticks a few boxes back in class and up in trip. CASINO ROYALE (1) is not out of this on recent performances.
